    "difficulty": "medium",
    "calculator": false,
    "isLatex": false,
    "format": "text",
    "question": "An ecosystem has a gross primary productivity (GPP) of 800 g C/m²/year and plant respiration accounts for 300 g C/m²/year. What is the net primary productivity (NPP), and what does it represent?",
