    "question": "A family living in an older home in a northern climate notices that several family members frequently experience headaches and fatigue, especially during winter months when windows are kept closed. Testing reveals elevated levels of radon gas in the basement. Which of the following best explains the source of radon, why symptoms worsen in winter, and an appropriate mitigation strategy?",
