      "C) The student is incorrect because stratospheric ozone depletion from CFCs increases UV-B radiation globally, not just over Antarctica, raising risks of skin cancer, cataracts, and ecosystem damage worldwide; the Montreal Protocol addressed a globally distributed atmospheric threat requiring international cooperation that domestic legislation like the Clean Air Act could not achieve alone.",
