    "isLatex": false,
    "format": "text",
    "question": "A developing nation rapidly increases electricity generation by building new coal-fired power plants to support economic growth. Which of the following would most likely be the immediate environmental consequence specifically related to CO2 emissions from this expansion?",
    "choices": [
      "A) Increased atmospheric CO2 concentrations contributing to enhanced greenhouse warming over time.",
      "B) Immediate and rapid cooling of the local region due to increased particulate matter reflecting sunlight.",
      "C) Depletion of the stratospheric ozone layer due to elevated CO2 reacting with ozone molecules.",
      "D) Accelerated ocean deoxygenation as CO2 directly binds with dissolved oxygen in seawater."
    ],
    "answer": 0,
