    "question": "In a coastal marine ecosystem, sea otters prey heavily on sea urchins. When sea otter populations decline due to hunting, sea urchin populations explode, and kelp forests are decimated because urchins overgraze kelp. Which of the following best explains this ecological dynamic and the role of sea otters?",
