    "question": "Two hypothetical countries, Country A and Country B, have identical age structures, identical mortality rates, and no net migration. Country A has a total fertility rate (TFR) of 2.1 and Country B has a TFR of 4.8. Given these conditions, which of the following statements best describes the long-term population outlook for each country?",
