    "question": "Researchers studying a heavily deforested region of the Amazon Basin observe that some areas experience intense flooding during the wet season while nearby areas suffer prolonged drought. Which of the following best explains this mixed precipitation pattern as a consequence of large-scale tropical deforestation?",
