      "B) EPA regulations under the Clean Air Act required the phase-out of leaded gasoline, targeting lead as a criteria air pollutant and dramatically reducing mobile source lead emissions.",
      "C) The Toxic Substances Control Act banned all lead-containing consumer products simultaneously in the 1970s, eliminating the major sources of human lead exposure.",
